\c 14
\s UAbrama ukhulula uLothi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ensukwini zikaAmrafeli inkosi yeShinari\x + 11.2.\x*, uAriyoki inkosi yeElasari, uKedolawoma inkosi yeElamu\x + 10.22. Isa. 11.11. Seb. 2.9.\x*, loTidali inkosi yezizwe,
\v 2 balwa impi loBera inkosi yeSodoma\x + 19.24.\x*, loBirisha inkosi yeGomora\x + 19.24.\x*, uShinabi inkosi yeAdima\x + Dute. 29.23.\x*, loShemebere inkosi yeZeboyimi\x + Dute. 29.23.\x*, lenkosi yeBhela, eliyiZowari\x + 14.8; 19.22.\x*.
\v 3 Bonke labo bahlangana esigodini iSidima esiluLwandle lweTswayi\x + Nani 34.12. Dute. 3.17. Josh. 3.16.\x*.
\v 4 Babemkhonzile uKedolawoma okweminyaka elitshumi lambili, kodwa ngomnyaka wetshumi lantathu bavukela.
\v 5 Langomnyaka wetshumi lane kweza uKedolawoma, lamakhosi ayelaye, batshaya amaRefa\x + 15.20. Dute. 3.11. Josh. 12.4; 13.12; 17.15. 2 Sam. 5.18,22; 23.13.\x* eAshiterothi-Karnayimi\x + Josh. 12.4; 13.12.\x*, lamaZuzi\x + Dute. 2.20.\x* eHamu, lamaEmi\x + Dute. 2.10,11.\x* egcekeni leKiriyathayimi,
\v 6 lamaHori entabeni yeSeyiri\x + 36.8,19. Dute. 2.12,22.\x*, kuze kube eEliparani\f + \fk iEliparani: \fl kumbe, \fq igceke leParani.\f* eliseduze lenkangala\x + 21.21. Nani 12.16.\x*.
\v 7 Basebebuyela bafika eEnimishipati eliyiKadeshi, batshaya ilizwe lonke lamaAmaleki, njalo lamaAmori ayehlala eHazazoni-Tamari\x + 2 Lan. 20.2.\x*.
\v 8 Kwasekuphuma inkosi yeSodoma lenkosi yeGomora, lenkosi yeAdima lenkosi yeZeboyimi, lenkosi yeBhela eliyiZowari, bahlomisa impi labo esigodini iSidima,
\v 9 emelane loKedolawoma inkosi yeElamu, loTidali inkosi yezizwe, loAmrafeli inkosi yeShinari, loAriyoki inkosi yeElasari; amakhosi amane emelane lamakhosi amahlanu.
\v 10 Lesigodi seSidima sasilemigodigodi yengcino\x + 11.3.\x*, lenkosi yeSodoma leyeGomora abaleka, awela khona; lasalayo abalekela entabeni\x + 19.17,30.\x*,
\v 11 asethatha yonke impahla yeSodoma leyeGomora\x + 14.16,21.\x*, lokudla kwabo bonke, ahamba.
\v 12 Amthatha loLothi lempahla yakhe, indodana yomfowabo kaAbrama\x + 12.5.\x*, asehamba, ngoba wayehlala eSodoma\x + 13.12.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kwasekusiza owayephunyukile, wamlandisela uAbrama umHeberu, owayehlala ezihlahleni zamaokhi* zeMamre\x + 13.18.\x* umAmori, umfowabo kaEshikoli lomfowabo kaAneri ababelesivumelwano loAbrama\x + 14.24.\x*.
\v 14 Kwathi uAbrama esezwile ukuthi umfowabo uthunjiwe\x + 13.8.\x*, wahlomisa\f + \fk wahlomisa: \fl kumbe, \fq wakhokhela.\f* ayebafundisile, bezelwe endlini yakhe\x + 12.5,16; 15.3; 17.12,13,23,27. Tshu. 2.7.\x*, abangamakhulu amathathu letshumi lesificaminwembili, waxotshana \add lawo\add* waze wafika koDani\x + Dute. 34.1. Hlu. 18.29.\x*.
\v 15 Wasezehlukanisa emelane lawo ebusuku, yena lenceku zakhe, wawatshaya, waxotshana lawo waze wafika eHoba, ekwesokhohlo seDamaseko\x + 1 Sam. 23.19,24. Eks. 26.18,35; 27.9; 36.23; 38.9.\x*.
\v 16 Wasebuyisa yonke impahla, njalo loLothi umfowabo lempahla yakhe, labesifazana labo labantu.
\s UMelkizedeki ubusisa uAbrama
\p
\v 17 Inkosi yeSodoma yasiphuma ukumhlangabeza, esebuyile ekutshayeni uKedolawoma lamakhosi ayelaye, esigodini iShave, esiyisigodi senkosi\x + 2 Sam. 18.18.\x*.
\v 18 UMelkizedeki inkosi yeSalema\x + Heb. 7.1.\x* waseletha isinkwa lewayini; njalo yena ngumpristi\x + Hlab. 110.4. Heb. 5.6.\x* kaNkulunkulu oPhezukonke\x + Seb. 16.17.\x*.
\v 19 Wasembusisa wathi: Kabusiswe uAbrama nguNkulunkulu\x + Ruthe 3.10. 2 Sam. 2.5.\x* oPhezukonke, uMnini wamazulu lomhlaba\x + 14.22.\x*.
\v 20 Kabusiswe-ke uNkulunkulu\x + 24.27.\x* oPhezukonke onikele izitha zakho esandleni sakho. Wasemnika ingxenye yetshumi yakho konke\x + Heb. 7.4. Gen. 28.22.\x*.
\v 21 Inkosi yeSodoma yasisithi kuAbrama: Nginika abantu\f + \fk abantu: \fl Heb. \fq imiphefumulo.\f*, kodwa uzithathele impahla.
\v 22 UAbrama wasesithi eN\sc KOSI\sc*ni yeSodoma: Ngiphakamise isandla sami\x + Dan. 12.7. Isam. 10.5,6. Eks. 6.8. Dute. 32.40. Nani 14.30. Hez. 20.5.6.\x* eN\sc KOSI\sc*ni uNkulunkulu oPhezukonke, uMnini wamazulu lomhlaba,
\v 23 ngithi kangiyikuthatha kusukela kumucu kusiya emchilweni wenyathela\x + Esta 9.15,16.\x*, kukho konke olakho! Hlezi uthi: Mina ngimnothisile uAbrama.
\v 24 Ngaphandle kwalokho kuphela akudlileyo amajaha, lesabelo samadoda ahambe lami\x + 14.13.\x*, uAneri, uEshikoli loMamre, bona kabathathe isabelo sabo.
